xiv - X11 image viewer
=============================

xiv is a  X11 image viewer. It reads images (in the farbfeld format)
from either stdin or from a list of command-line arguments and displays them
in an X11 window.


Features
--------

- view modes:
  - original image size.
  - stretch image to window, keep aspect ratio.
  - stretch image to window, don't keep aspect ratio.
- keybinds
- zooming
- panning


Dependencies
------------

- libX11


Optional (run-time) dependencies
--------------------------------

- farbfeld: https://github.com/k1574/ff


Installation and compilation
----------------------------

About it you can read at
https://github.com/k1574/install


